# Paleta (light)
- Primary 700 **#083044** (headers, nav, footer)
- Primary 600 **#0E4A69** (botón primario)
- Accent 600 **#1FA5B8** (acciones secundarias/links destacados)
- Neutral 900 **#0B1220** (texto)
- Neutral 100 **#F4F6F8** (fondos sutiles)
- White **#FFFFFF**
- Feedback: Success **#0E9F6E**, Warning **#B45309**, Error **#B91C1C**

# Paleta (dark)
- Background **#0B1220**, Foreground **#F7FAFC**
- Primary **#1FA5B8**, Primary-foreground **#061923**
- Accent **#0E4A69**, Accent-foreground **#E6F7FA**
- Surface **#121A2A** / Borde **#1E293B**

# Tipografía
- Headings: **IBM Plex Serif**; Body/UI: **Inter**.
- Body: 16–18px, `line-height` 1.5–1.65; ancho de lectura `~65ch`.

